pull_request.title: Remove constant time issue files for SIKE
pull_request.body: The suppression files for constant time warnings in SIKE are no longer necessary, as all of the known problems have been fixed. Thanks to @bhess for pointing this out https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/issues/892#issuecomment-831181293.

pull_request.title: Add canaries around malloc'd regions in test_sig
pull_request.body:
#986 inadvertently broke test_constant_time by using memcmp on some canaries in test_kem. This PR disables the canary checks when OQS_ENABLE_TEST_CONSTANT_TIME=ON.

More importantly, this PR adds canaries to test_sig. I followed #986 in using an odd length for the canaries in the hope of catching alignment bugs.
